title: Quickload Database Update CD v3.8
description:
THIS IS NOT a Quickload v3.8 installer. You will need QuickLOAD already installed in order to run this update. This will update Quickload v3.0 - v3.8 database (powders, bullets, etc) to the January 12, 2014 v3.8 database.

Instructions:

1. Already have Quickload installed on your Windows PC.
2. Either burn ISO to CD/DVD or mount ISO using MagicDisk (free), Daemon Tools (Shareware), etc.
3. Run Qupdate.exe and follow prompts
4. If running pirated software, please purchase Quickload to help support programmers. :)
5. Happy reloading.
